room_title: Escape room "Welcome to Enigma High" by Enter The Enigma in Colorado Springs
room_address: 3540 N. Academy Blvd Colorado Springs, CO 80917
room_description: A brain, a beauty, a jock, a rebel and a recluse…..which one will you be? Or Will You Be Clueless? It's Saturday detention and the day is almost done when you hear a car leave the parking lot. It was the Vice-Principal! Checking the door, you realize he forgot you were all here. Now if you don’t want to spend the entire weekend at school you must work together to ensure your escape. Room is a tribute to the high school movies/tv shows of the past 40 years.
